Name: assign_worker_to_task
Description: Whether a worker is assigned to a task

Name: select_feature_for_sprint
Description: Whether a feature is selected for the sprint backlog

Name: set_sprint_duration
Description: Duration of the sprint in weeks

Name: allocate_budget_to_project
Description: Amount of budget allocated to a project

Name: assign_skill_to_worker
Description: Whether a skill is assigned to a worker

Name: set_task_effort
Description: Estimated effort for a task in story points

Name: select_user_story_for_sprint
Description: Whether a user story is selected for the sprint backlog

Name: assign_scrum_master_to_team
Description: Whether a scrum master is assigned to a team

Name: set_release_plan_date
Description: Planned release date for a release plan
